Calibration: Calibrations of the time for the ToF
system and the energy for the SSD were performed by
measuring the elastically scattered 16O and 18O ions
from a 209Bi target, and also the particles recoiling
out from thin targets, natural Ag, natural In, natural
Sb by bombardment of the 350 MeV 127I beam.
Used as ToF telescope at theta(lab)=60 deg
To measure kinetic energies of fission
Set at theta(lab)=99 deg. Solid angle was 80
Data are received by e-mail from I.Nishinaka
